name: Conditions_T2DM
title: conditions_T2DM
purpose: (Clinical Focus: Codes that represent Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus),(Data Element Scope: SNOMED CT concepts and billable ICD-10-CM concepts that indicate the presence of type 2 diabetes mellitus),(Inclusion Criteria: Any SNOMED CT concept or billable ICD-10-CM code that indicates the presences of type 2 diabetes mellitus),(Exclusion Criteria: Codes not specific for type 2 diabetes mellitus (including those for other forms of diabetes))
